{"url": "www.brides.com/story/katie-holmes-wedding-ring-jamie-foxx", "text": "Key Takeaways Hollywood celebrities often spend millions on engagement rings, with prices ranging from $1 million to over $38 million.\n\nSome stars, like Paris Hilton and Jennifer Lopez, have received multiple million-dollar engagement rings over their lifetimes.\n\nFamous engagement rings, such as Grace Kelly's, have increased in value over time due to inflation and rarity.\n\nWith an average cost of $6,500 to $7,000, engagement rings are known to be relatively expensive pieces of jewelry. Compared to the amount of money that celebrities drop on their respective partners\u2019 baubles, though, this standard price seems negligible. With a large budget to work with, Hollywood stars, world-renowned athletes, and high-status royals often purchase enormous sparklers that come with an equally massive price tag.\n\nWhile the exact cost of every celebrity engagement ring throughout history isn\u2019t known, jewelry experts have used their expertise and experience to estimate the cost of many stars\u2019 baubles. With their approximations, we compiled a list of famous individuals who have the most expensive sparklers to date. While some of these lavish jewels were marked with a multimillion-dollar price tag, others increased in value over time, thanks to inflation.\n\nFrom $1 million to over $38 million, here are 25 of the priciest celebrity engagement rings of all time, from the least costly to most costly. Keep scrolling to see which stars flaunt (or once flaunted) the most valuable pieces of jewelry on their left ring finger.\n\n", "images": ["https://www.brides.com/thmb/GgPr_K15Mt48qfXvTdxsPSEJOPg=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/most-expensive-celebrity-engagement-rings-jennifer-aniston-getty-images-ea00e4fef68745ce9dbdeef0b22971d9.jpg", "https://www.brides.com/thmb/NSFXWx5FxtAjY03Y2T2TbYkvLT4=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/ku-df4b2777e0b